headline: JPMorgan lowers HP to Neutral on tough near-term outlook, shares drop
summary: Investing.com -- JPMorgan has downgraded HP Inc. to Neutral from Overweight, saying the company is entering a more challenging phase as it moves past the most favorable part of the PC volume and cost cycle.
